pageTitle: Ohaus school digital scales and mechanical balances
textBeforeTable: New Valor 5000 from Ohaus is a checkweighing scale featuring a spill resistant design. Valor-5000 features multiple weighing modes including percent weighing, static weighing, positive/zero/negative static checkweighing. Checkweighing is made easy, whether you need to use the Valor 5000 for packaging or you plan to use this food scale for portioning out of the box there is a separate checkweighing mode for each.
